    <entry>
      <title>建立任何类型链表</title>
      <link href="2020/11/14/2020-11-12-lianbiao/"/>
      <url>2020/11/14/2020-11-12-lianbiao/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="结构体的定义"><a href="#结构体的定义" class="headerlink" title="结构体的定义"></a>结构体的定义</h2><ol><li>当结构体使用如下定义一个指向结构的指针时。</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">struct node</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int value;</span><br><span class="line">struct node *next;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; *NODE;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在使用NODE这个结构体指针时需要分配内存，即在函数中需要对NODE分配内存才能使用。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int main(void)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">NODE&#x3D;(node *)malloc(sizeof(struct node)) &#x2F;&#x2F;并强转为指向node的指针</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><ol start="2"><li>当结构体使用typedef 把结构体指针重新定义为一种结构体指针时（也就是使用typedef 把结构体指针重新定义为一种类型，这个类型就是**==链表==**）</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">typedef struct node</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int value;</span><br><span class="line">struct node *next;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; *NODE;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>使用这个链表（现在这个链表是一种类型，不能直接使用，要使用此类型定义一个链表变量)时，NODE lianbiao;最重要的是对这个链表分配动态内存并强转为链表对应的类型。（因为此变量是NODE类型，所以强转时变为NODE类型）</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int main(void)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">NODE lianbiao;</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao&#x3D;(NODE)malloc(sizeof(struct node));</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;接下来就可以使用lianbiao了</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li><p>当使用#define定义一种可以创建任何类型的链表时，要使用 define 和typedef同时使用 define 要替换的内容必须在同一行（如果替换的内容覆盖多行，必须使用连字符，即“\”</p><p><strong>定义一种链表后，也必须先用这种链表类型定义一个变量，然后对变量分配动态内存并强转为这个变量对应的链表类型</strong></p></li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#define LIST(T) typedef struct node&#123;T value;struct node *next;&#125; *NODE;</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;使用define的替换功能定义一种可以时任何类型的链表（通过参量T输入想要的类型）</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;define所替换的内容必须在同一行如果替换的内容覆盖多行可以使用连字符,即 “\”。上面的那句可以替换成下面的写法</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#define LIST(T) typedef \</span><br><span class="line">struct node\</span><br><span class="line">&#123;\</span><br><span class="line">T value;\</span><br><span class="line">struct node *next;\</span><br><span class="line">&#125; *NODE;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下面时如何使用各种类型的链表</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int main(void)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">LIST(int);&#x2F;&#x2F;被替换成typedef struct node&#123;int value;struct node *next;&#125; *NODE;      int链表类型定义</span><br><span class="line">NODE lianbiao; 使用int类型链表，定义一个链表（变量）。</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao&#x3D;(NODE)malloc(sizeof(struct node));&#x2F;&#x2F;对这个链表（变量）分配动态内存，并强转为NODE类型的链表（强转为定义这个链表（变量）的类型）</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;下面使用这个链表</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao-&gt;value&#x3D;8;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;%d&quot;,lianbiao-&gt;value);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">LIST(char);&#x2F;&#x2F;被替换为typedef struct node&#123;char value;struct node *next;&#125; *NODE;  char链表类型定义</span><br><span class="line">NODE lianbiao1; &#x2F;&#x2F;使用char类型链表，定义一个链表（变量）。</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao1&#x3D;(NODE)malloc(sizeof(struct node));&#x2F;&#x2F;对这个链表（变量）分配动态内存，并强转为NODE类型的链表（强转为定义这个链表（变量）的类型）</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;下面使用这个链表</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao1-&gt;value&#x3D;&#39;a&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;%c&quot;,lianbiao1-&gt;value);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">typedef int nihao;</span><br><span class="line">LIST(nihao);&#x2F;&#x2F;被替换为typedef struct node&#123;nihao value;struct node *next;&#125; *NODE;  nihao链表类型定义</span><br><span class="line">NODE lianbiao2; &#x2F;&#x2F;使用char类型链表，定义一个链表（变量）。</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao2&#x3D;(NODE)malloc(sizeof(struct node));&#x2F;&#x2F;对这个链表（变量）分配动态内存，并强转为NODE类型的链表（强转为定义这个链表（变量）的类型）</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;下面使用这个链表</span><br><span class="line">nihao a;</span><br><span class="line">scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;a);</span><br><span class="line">lianbiao2-&gt;value&#x3D;a;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;%d&quot;,lianbiao2-&gt;value);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意上面三条LIST(T) 不能同时出现在同一个函数，不然会报错重定义NODE</strong></p><p>下面时这三个链表建立和使用的程序，<a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xinminwang/picture-host/main/document/2020-11-12-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8.cpp">下载文件</a></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xinminwang/picture-host/main/image/2020-11-12-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8.png" alt="2020-11-12-建立任何类型的链表"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
